# Documentation Authoring

**Before creating/editing docs:** read `docs/09-development/DOCUMENTATION_AUTHORING_RULES.md`

## Must

- Link new doc in `docs/README.md` (once, no duplicates)
- Align entity fields with EXCELLENCE §8 + SOFT-DELETE-POLICY + related Tasks
- ADR for architecture decisions — before implementation docs
- Header: status, version, related ADRs
- Error paths + edge cases — not happy-path only

## Soft delete in docs

All business entities: base fields + soft delete. Exceptions explicit (AuditLog, Outbox, Redis TTL).

## Sync

Doc change → update matching `Phases/.../TASK-*.md` if affected

## Review gate

Self-score ≥ **95/100** using rubric in DOCUMENTATION_AUTHORING_RULES §9 before Approved

## Full rules

`docs/09-development/DOCUMENTATION_AUTHORING_RULES.md`
